    "toxic": {
        "summary": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div>\n   <strong>Black nightshade is extremely toxic</strong> to cats and dogs. Ingesting any part of the plant, especially unripened berries, triggers symptoms like vomiting, diarrhea, weakness, confusion, seizures, and possibly paralysis. <strong>Fatalities in children have been reported</strong> due to unripe berries. Veterinary care is essential for animals and immediate medical attention is advised if ingestion is suspected.\n  </div> \n </body>\n</html>",
